  "prompt": "Where can you find some build examples for Titan Quest?",
  "response": "There are several sources where you can find build examples for Titan Quest, including:\n\n1. **Online Guide Websites:** Websites like GameFAQs, IGN, and others often have detailed guides and build examples written by experienced players.\n\n2. **Titan Quest Forums:** The official Titan Quest forums and other community forums like Steam Community or Reddit can be great places to find build discussions and examples shared by passionate players.\n\n3. **YouTube:** Many content creators and gamers post build guides and videos showcasing different character builds on YouTube. Channels dedicated to Titan Quest can provide detailed breakdowns of the skill sets and equipment needed.\n\n4. **Titan Quest Wiki:** Fan-created wikis often have detailed information on character builds, including recommended skills, masteries, and equipment.\n\n5. **Discord Communities:** Joining Discord servers dedicated to Titan Quest can give you access to real-time discussions and advice from other players who can share their favorite builds.\n\n6. **ARPG Fansites:** General ARPG (action role-playing game) fansites might include sections dedicated to Titan Quest, offering build suggestions and other game-related advice.\n\nExploring these resources can help you find a wide variety of builds suited to your playstyle and preferences.",
